Welcome to Snake Survival Game!

In this adaptation of the traditional Snake game, collect fruit to gain health while trying to escape
an ever-growing AI snake opponent.

Do you have what it takes to survive?

Controls:
<  left
>  right
^  up
v  down



Original game inspired and adapted from Bro Code's Snake Game Tutorial on YouTube:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bI6e6qjJ8JQ